sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant QC as QuizController
    participant Q as Question

    B->>QC: POST /quiz/play<br>(answer_id)
    QC->>Q: fetchAnswer(answer_id)
    Q-->>QC: return answer
    QC->>Q: fetchCorrectAnswer(question_id)
    Q-->>QC: return correct answer
    Note over QC: Prüft is_correct,<br>aktualisiert score/xp/wrong_answers in Session
    QC->>Q: saveResult(isCorrect, question_id, answer_id, quizId)
    Note over QC: Erhöht counter<br>Fragen verbleibend: Redirect /quiz/play<br>Letzte Frage: Redirect /quiz/result
    QC-->>B: Redirect /quiz/play oder /quiz/result